&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MDgxMzM2OQ==&amp;amp;mid=2649747185&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=4440935f4bf0c2b14777b957eb80afcd&amp;amp;chksm=881ea827bf692131a196e2ab42072fb366eefd5bea1632c6aad8dfd5399a1363fe9466a673b4&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-itemshowtype=&quot;0&quot; data-linktype=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;科技加市场化，能为方言续命吗？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



